file: template/rust-toolchain.toml
behavior: Pins the Rust toolchain version and required components (rustfmt, clippy) for building this project, using rustup's minimal profile.
edit_notes:
  - Version updates must be intentional; re-run the full clippy lint list against the new toolchain since restriction lint names occasionally change between releases.
functions:
invariants:
  - channel is fixed at "1.95.0"; components always include rustfmt and clippy.
external_deps:
  - rustup: reads this file to select the active toolchain and install rustfmt/clippy.